Mix @red wine{1%bottle}, @whole cardamom{20}, @cloves{12}, @cinnamon{4%stick}, @ginger{1%tbsp}(grated), @star anise{2}, @sugar{400%g}. Heat it until it steams but doesn't boil.

Let it cook on low heat for ~{40%minutes}. Strain and add @?rum{2%dl} and/or @?water{1-2%dl}.

Serve and garnish with @?raisins{}, @?almonds{} and @?orange slices{}.